用三个形容词来形容你自己？

225
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:23,520
I'm extroverted, I'm diligent, and I'm open-minded.
我性格外向，勤奋努力，而且思想开放。

226
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,520
Yeah.
是的。

227
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,520
That's awesome.
太棒了。

228
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,520
See?
看到了吧？

229
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,520
You sound really professional when you say things like this.
你这样说的时候听起来真的很专业。

230
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,520
Give me the job.
把这份工作给我。

231
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,520
Yeah.
是的。

232
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,520
Exactly.
没错。

233
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:35,440
So and even if you took a look at some of the negative adjectives that we used, it's
所以，即使你看了我们用过的一些负面形容词，也是这样的。

234
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:39,160
also a typical job interview question is like, what are your biggest faults?
还有一个典型的面试问题是，你最大的缺点是什么？

235
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:45,360
So you can say, well, maybe I am superstitious and naive.
所以你可以说，嗯，也许我既迷信又天真。

236
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:47,840
You wouldn't want to say that in a job interview.
你在面试时肯定不会这么说。

237
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,400
But I mean, I don't know, maybe.
但我是说，我也不确定，也许吧。

238
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,640
Because you have to say something, right?
因为你总得说点什么，对吧？

239
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:52,640
You do.
你确实有。

240
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:59,240
But I would say, sometimes I'm a bit too daring or sometimes I take things personally.
但我觉得吧，有时候我有点太大胆了，或者有时候太容易把事往心里去。

241
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,960
So we can talk about that another time.
那我们改天再聊这个。

242
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:05,480
But I think for now, it'd be good if we listened to today's dialogue one more time and really
不过我觉得现在最好再听一遍今天的对话，真正

243
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:10,360
got a good sense of how to use these words.
掌握这些词的用法。

244
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:16,920
Okay, class, settle down.
好了，同学们，安静下来。

245
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:20,040
I have the results of your individual personality tests.
我拿到了你们个人性格测试的结果。

246
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:21,760
I am going to hand them out.
我会把它们发下去。

247
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:24,920
And if you'd like, you can read them out loud to the rest of the class.
如果你们愿意，可以大声读给全班同学听。

248
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:25,920
I'll read mine.
我来读我的。

249
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:27,620
Okay, go ahead.
好的，请吧。

250
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:31,380
It says here that I am adventurous, outgoing, and easygoing.
上面说我爱冒险、外向、随和。

251
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:35,400
It says that I'm a little superstitious and occasionally naive.
还说我有点迷信，偶尔天真。

252
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,400
That's not true.
那不是真的。

253
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:39,800
Well, the test isn't 100% accurate.
嗯，这个测试不是百分之百准确。

254
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,200
Is that all it says?
就这些吗？

255
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,200
No.
不。

256
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:46,760
It also says that I'm open-minded with great ambition, but that I can also be reckless
还说我有开阔的胸怀和远大的抱负，但有时也鲁莽

257
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:48,380
and clumsy.
和笨拙。

258
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:49,680
This is stupid.
这太蠢了。

259
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:52,640
Okay, anyone else want to read theirs?
好了，还有谁想读自己的？

260
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,640
I'll go.
我来。

261
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:56,360
It says that I'm an extroverted, well-balanced person.
上面说我是一个外向、平衡的人。

262
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:59,440
It says I am generous, outspoken, and very diligent.
说我慷慨、直言不讳、非常勤奋。

263
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,840
This is so true.
这太准了。

264
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:04,560
It also says that I am a magnanimous, eloquent, and daring.
还说我宽宏大量、口才好、勇敢。

265
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,520
This is totally me.
这完全就是我。

266
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,640
Whatever.
随便吧。

267
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:10,560
These tests are baloney.
这些测试都是胡扯。

268
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:16,920
Alright, we're back.
好了，我们回来了。

269
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:21,200
So now going into descriptions.
现在进入描述部分。

270
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:27,020
What are three adjectives that you would use to describe someone that you hate the most?
你会用哪三个形容词来描述你最讨厌的人？

271
00:12:27,020 --> 00:12:33,640
So going back to describing people, how would you describe one of the main things that really
回到描述人的话题，你会怎么描述别人身上最让你

